      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a cracked taillight lens. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the suspension is starting to feel loose, and there is a slow oil leak that will eventually need attention. It\u2019s a solid candidate for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind performing some minor repairs and cosmetic touch-ups.",
